{"id":"172338516139198_540979405941772","from":{"name":"Eslam Hamouda","id":"10210277573008432"},"message":"7 Things Don't Use It If You Are Building a Trial Desktop App.\n\n1- Don't Encrypt/Decrypt Using Base64 Or Cipher Only (Mix Them) \n2- Don't Check The Equality Of The License Using If (Use Switch)\n3- Don't Make The Check Of License Offline (Use API)\n4- Don't Send/Receive Plain Text Over The API Calls (Encrypt All)\n5- Don't Store The License Info On The Machine (Store It Online)\n6- Don't Calculate The Trial Period Based On User Machine (Use The Server Time)\n7- Don't Publish Your App Directly After The Final Build (Obfuscate It)\n\n• This Based On Personal Experience Throw The Last Week While Am Trying To Reset The Trial Period Of Some Visual Studio Extensions , And Failed ! :D","actions":[{"name":"Comment","link":"https://www.facebook.com/172338516139198/posts/540979405941772"},{"name":"Like","link":"https://www.facebook.com/172338516139198/posts/540979405941772"},{"name":"Report Post to Admin","link":"https://www.facebook.com/groups/egyptian.geeks/members/"}],"privacy":{"value":"","description":"","friends":"","allow":"","deny":""},"type":"status","created_time":"2013-03-13T04:58:16+0000","updated_time":"2013-03-13T19:02:14+0000","is_hidden":false,"is_expired":false,"likes":{"data":[{"id":"10212736613196934","name":"Mohamed Elnagar"},{"id":"1453218434709440","name":"Wajdy Essam"},{"id":"1351989794859335","name":"Abdulrahman Mohamed"}],"paging":{"cursors":{"before":"MTAyMTI3MzY2MTMxOTY5MzQZD","after":"MTM1MTk4OTc5NDg1OTMzNQZDZD"}}},"comments":{"data":[{"created_time":"2013-03-13T08:08:36+0000","from":{"name":"Shady M. Najib","id":"10154838763611066"},"message":"Watch a couple of these videos, and you'd know that most of that is still \"hackable\" :)\n\nhttp://www.digitalbodyguard.com/speechvideo.html","can_remove":false,"like_count":1,"user_likes":false,"id":"541014652604914"},{"created_time":"2013-03-13T08:42:30+0000","from":{"name":"Mohamed Elsherif","id